                "https://feddit.uk/pictrs/image/4ef6c72c-a4aa-4374-9402-4e1018d75544.webp",
              description: "A UK centric gateway into the fediverse.",
              icon: "https://feddit.uk/pictrs/image/1108a696-0e37-442e-aade-3a9b6f828d75.webp",
              id: 1,
              inbox_url: "https://feddit.uk/inbox",
              instance_id: 1,
              last_refreshed_at: "2023-06-09T08:34:11.814022Z",
              name: "Feddit UK",
              public_key: "",
              published: "2023-06-09T08:29:16.797362Z",
              sidebar:
                '### Who are we?\nFeddit.uk is UK-centric, with integration to the wider Fediverse.   \n  We tend to focus on UK-interest communities, others are welcome.\n\n  The name is a shortening of "federate it".  \n  Want to share a thing? Share it with the fediverse, or, fed-it.  \n- See it\n- Like it?\n- Feddit\n\n### What are the rules here?\n* No racism, sexism, homophobia, transphobia or xenophobia\n  * See our [guidelines on transphobia](https://guide.feddit.uk/politics/transphobia.html) for more detail\n* No incitement of violence or promotion of violent ideologies\n* No harassment, dogpiling or doxxing of other users\n* Do not share intentionally false or misleading information\n* Do not spam or abuse network features.\n* Alt accounts are permitted, but all accounts must list each other in their bios. \n* No generative AI content\n\nRules apply on this instance, and when using an account from this instance to interact with other instances.  \n  Administrators may warn or ban for breaches of the rules, or the spirit of the rules.\n\n### Where should I start?\n\nIf you are new, say "hello" over at !welcome@feddit.uk. We can offer any specific help you might need there. Other than that...\n\n#### Here\n- !unitedkingdom@feddit.uk for general UK news.\n- !casualuk@feddit.uk for general chit-chat.\n- !uk_politics@feddit.uk for politics.\n- !memes@feddit.uk to watch us get arrested for stealing memes without a licence.\n- !askuk@feddit.uk to find out where to get a meme licence.\n- !andfinally@feddit.uk for silly news.\n\n#### Elsewhere\n- [Lemmyverse > communities](https://lemmyverse.net/communities)\n- !newtolemmy@lemmy.ca\n\n### Frontends\n\n* [Photon](https://p.feddit.uk/)\n* [Alexandrite](https://a.feddit.uk/)\n* [Old](https://old.feddit.uk/)\n* [Blorp](https://b.feddit.uk/)\n\n### Donation Link\n\nThis site does not serve adverts.  \n  [![OpenCollective donate button](https://opencollective.com/feddituk/tiers/notier.svg?avatarHeight=72)](https://opencollective.com/feddituk)  \n  [![OpenCollective donor counter link](https://opencollective.com/feddituk/tiers/badge.svg)](https://opencollective.com/feddituk)\n\n### Contact \n\n[![Matrix](https://img.shields.io/matrix/feddit-uk-chat%3Amatrix.org?logo=matrix&amp%3BlogoColor=white&amp%3Blabel=Matrix)](https://matrix.to/#/#feddit.uk:matrix.org)\n\n### Uptime status\n* [UptimeRobot](https://stats.uptimerobot.com/XzEqqSB3Ay)\n* [Lemmy Meter](https://lemmy-meter.info/d/GeoFE5WIz/instance-health-breakdown?var-lemmy_instance=feddit.uk&amp%3Bkiosk=tv&amp%3BorgId=1)\n\n### Fediseer\n[![Fediseer guarantees](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/badges/guarantees/feddit.uk.svg)](https://gui.fediseer.com/instances/detail/feddit.uk)\n\n[![Fediseer endorsements](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/badges/endorsements/feddit.uk.svg)](https://gui.fediseer.com/instances/detail/feddit.uk)\n\n### Threads\n\nMeta\'s activitypub network has been blocked as a default.  \n  If you believe there is a good case for this not to be, please start a thread in the feddit.uk community.\n\n### Banner\n\nCredit for the iconic banner --> https://joelgoodman.net/',
