              published: "2023-06-06T23:25:23.202595Z",
              sidebar:
                '## About Us\n\n- Reddthat [rules](https://reddthat.com/post/9701)\n- Signups Open\n- Email Optional\n- Downvotes Disabled\n- Image & Videos allowed (Up to 20MB)\n- Our status page: https://status.reddthat.com/ \n\n## Official Communities\nThese are the communities that are specifically for Reddthat users in some "Official" way. There are plenty of other equally important communities that call Reddthat home and can be found [here](https://reddthat.com/communities?listingType=Local&sort=TopMonth&page=1).\n\n::: spoiler Communities (Click to show)\n- Announcements Community:  !reddthat@reddthat.com\n- Reddthat Offtopic Community: !community@reddthat.com \n  - Why not make your first post here!\n:::\n\n\n## Alternate Web Interfaces\nThese are 3rd party applications hosted on the Reddthat infrastructure.\n::: spoiler Alternate Web Interfaces (Click to show)\n  - Photon: https://photon.reddthat.com/\n  - Voyager: https://voyager.reddthat.com/ (Mobile specific)\n  - "Old": https://old.reddthat.com/ (You might be familiar with this layout)\n:::\n\n\n## Funding\nOur instance is 100% community-funded. For more information read: [Funding &amp; Longevity](https://reddthat.com/post/25633) or click a donation link below!\n\n[![Liberapay donate button. Please donate, the server needs food](https://liberapay.com/assets/widgets/donate.svg)](https://liberapay.com/reddthat/donate) - ![Image showing how many supporters Reddthat has](https://img.shields.io/liberapay/patrons/reddthat.svg?logo=liberapay)\n\n::: spoiler Donation Links (Click to show)\n- LiberaPay: https://liberapay.com/reddthat\n- Ko-Fi: https://ko-fi.com/reddthat\n- Crypto:\n  - [Donate Crypto (Trocador)](https://trocador.app/anonpay/?ticker_to=xmr&network_to=Mainnet&address=4286pC9NxdyTo5Y3Z9Yr9NN1PoRUE3aXnBMW5TeKuSzPHh6eYB6HTZk7W9wmAfPqJR1j684WNRkcHiP9TwhvMoBrUD9PSt3&donation=True&simple_mode=True&amount=0.0002&name=Reddthat&buttonbgcolor=9f6c59&bgcolor=9f6c59aa)\n  - [Donate Crypto (Trocador Onion)](http://trocadorfyhlu27aefre5u7zri66gudtzdyelymftvr4yjwcxhfaqsid.onion/anonpay/?ticker_to=xmr&network_to=Mainnet&address=4286pC9NxdyTo5Y3Z9Yr9NN1PoRUE3aXnBMW5TeKuSzPHh6eYB6HTZk7W9wmAfPqJR1j684WNRkcHiP9TwhvMoBrUD9PSt3&donation=True&simple_mode=True&amount=0.0002&name=Reddthat&buttonbgcolor=9f6c59&bgcolor=9f6c59aa)\n- XMR Directly: `4286pC9NxdyTo5Y3Z9Yr9NN1PoRUE3aXnBMW5TeKuSzPHh6eYB6HTZk7W9wmAfPqJR1j684WNRkcHiP9TwhvMoBrUD9PSt3`\n- LTC Directly: `ltc1qfs92f6d80jelhj6avwf9u7q5p7ldqqzg0twunw`\n:::\n\n## Thankyou\n\nThank-you for joining our little community. Because, without **you**, this community wouldn\'t be what it is today. \n\n‚ù§Ô∏è Tiff ',
